  <brief_title>A Multiple Ascending Dose Study of ETC-1002 in Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multiple Ascending Dose Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of ETC-1002 at Doses Above 120 mg/Day in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
