  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Phase 1, double-blind (sponsor open), placebo controlled study will assess the safety,
      tolerability, pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics of multiple doses of ETC-1002 in healthy
      subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
